Visitors to '''[[Abkhazia]]''' must obtain a [[visa (document)|visa]] unless they come from one of the visa exempt countries.

== Visa policy map ==
[[File:Visa policy of Abkhazia.png|800px|thumbnail|center|Visa policy of Abkhazia]]

== Visa policy ==
Citizens of the following countries and territories can visit Abkhazia without a visa:<ref>[http://mfaapsny.org/council/visa.php Ministry of foreign affairs. Visa information.]</ref><ref>[http://presidentofabkhazia.org/upload/iblock/059/УКАЗ_безвизовый_въезд.PDF Decree of the President of Abkhazia. On the establishment of visa-free entry to the Republic of Abkhazia of certain categories of foreign citizens] (in Russian)</ref>

'''90 days'''
*{{flagicon|Ukraine}} [[Donetsk People's Republic|DNR]] and [[Luhansk People's Republic|LNR]] residents
*{{flag|Nicaragua}}
*{{flag|Russia}}
*{{flag|South Ossetia}}
*{{flag|Transnistria}}
*{{flag|Tuvalu}}

'''14 days''' 
*{{flag|Belarus}}
*{{flag|Kazakhstan}}

'''Tourism groups'''

Tourists from all countries (except Georgia) can visit Abkhazia for a period not exceeding 24 hours as part of an organized tourist group.

